// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-3522 — Mass File Rename (interlock)
// Status: test | Level: high | ID: 3efc4b5b-3b19-5b68-9289-c45346931919

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
